duaList.arabic: رَبِّ اغْفِـرْ لي ، رَبِّ اغْفِـرْ لي
duaList.translation: My Lord forgive me, My Lord forgive me.

duaList.arabic: اللّهُـمَّ اغْفِـرْ لي ، وَارْحَمْـني ، وَاهْدِنـي ، وَاجْبُرْنـي ، وَعافِنـي وَارْزُقْنـي وَارْفَعْـني
duaList.transliteration: Allahummagh-fir lee, warhamnee, wahdinee, wajburnee, waAAafinee, warzuqnee warfaAAnee.
duaList.translation: O Allah, forgive me, have mercy upon me, guide me, enrich me, give me health, grant me sustenance and raise my rank.
